      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic repairs. The engine currently runs roughly with several visible fluid leaks, and the transmission shifts are quite harsh. Externally, the body shows significant wear, including noticeable rust and various dents, while the interior requires substantial restoration. This is an ideal project for someone looking for a parts car or a complete overhaul, sold strictly as-is.",
